name: Grabity
public_notice: Grabity has performed at token migration from 0xcbd49182346421d3b410b04aeb1789346da6ce43 to 0x30634241d3A7FbCea55f0Ba7dF42dFD8CDd8B2Cd.

description.en:
Grabity is a public blockchain that assists blockchain businesses to build the network in the mobile environment easily and aims to lead the Internet paradigm through decentralization. As an open project, Grabity focuses on developing a background to build dApps for developers.

The open source project aims to become a standardized protocol among public blockchains by utilizing unused computing resources. In the Orbits Network, developers can build dApps without paying any transaction fees in the ecosystem. Because of this, the waste of computing resources and energy can be reduced.

Grabity is currently servicing the Planet Wallet that users can customize their wallet as a unique planet supporting hassle-free transactions. The Grabity Foundation releases the Planet Wallet SDK for developers as open sources.

The decentralized project highlights the role of its developer’s community who join the open source development community and also the governance council with voting rights.
